FBIS4-42713 "drweu109__a94024" FBIS-WEU-94-109-A Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 ANNEX Switzerland UK Defense Secretary Visits 2-3 Jun UK Defense Secretary Visits 2-3 Jun AU0606160694 Zurich NEUE ZUERCHER ZEITUNG in German 6 Jun 94 p 25--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY AU0606160694 Zurich NEUE ZUERCHER ZEITUNG German BFN [SDA report: "Defense Secretary Rifkind Visits Switzerland"] [Text] On Thursday and Friday [2-3 June] British Defense Secretary Malcolm Rifkind discussed issues relating to security policy with Federal Councilor Kaspar Villiger. Rifkind explained that his country would welcome a Swiss blue helmet contingent and briefed Villiger on the missions of British blue helmets. Diplomatic efforts, peacekeeping operations, as well as humanitarian aid are extremely valuable measures that his country is implementing in armed conflicts all over the world. Villiger stated that after his conversation with Rifkind he sees his view again confirmed that, in particular, neutral states can provide important peacekeeping missions between the frontlines.
